graph TD
    A[New Agent Code / Prompt Change] --> B{Run Test Suite}
    
    subgraph Offline Evaluation (EDD)
    B --> C[Fetch 'Golden Dataset' from LangSmith]
    C --> D[Run Agent offline across 100 Scenarios]
    D -.->|Mock out live Web/DB tools| E[Simulated Tool Returns]
    E --> F[Agent Outputs]
    
    F --> G[Custom Evaluators]
    G -->|Exact Match| H[Scoring]
    G -->|LLM-as-a-Judge| H
    end
    
    H --> I{Did Aggregate Score Drop?}
    I -->|Yes - Regression!| J[Revert Prompt / Code Change]
    I -->|No - Improvement!| K[Deploy to Production]
